---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Indi Watte">
    <section class="about-me">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            Hi, I’m Indi Watte — a DEVINE student at Howest with a passion for
            combining design and technology to create meaningful digital
            experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
            My interests include creative coding, motion design, and exploring
            how people interact with digital products. I enjoy experimenting
            with tools like Astro, JavaScript, and p5.js to bring ideas to life
            on the web.
        </p>

        <img src="/src/assets/images/indi.jpeg" alt="">
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3>Skills & Tools</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
            <li>PHP Backend Development</li>
            <li>Astro & modern web frameworks</li>
            <li>Creative coding with p5.js</li>
            <li>UI/UX designing</li>
            <li>Visual Design & Adobe Tools</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3>What I’m currently working on</h3>
        <p>
            Building my personal portfolio with Astro and diving deeper into
            responsive design is an interesting and rewarding project. It’s not
            only a chance to explore responsiveness and sharpen my Git skills,
            but also a way to organize and showcase two years of learning,
            growth, challenges, creativity, and moments of both frustration and
            satisfaction.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3>My Work as a DEVINE student</h3>
        <p>
            Here’s a quick look at some of my projects that explore design,
            animation, and creative coding. Each project reflects my process of
            learning, experimenting, and refining my work as always
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
        </ul>

        <a href="/projects" class="button">View All Projects</a>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* Wrapper spacing for sections */
    section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Headings */
    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    /* Paragraphs */
    p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Lists */
    ul {
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    /* Button */
    .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
        background: #fff;
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .button:hover {
        background: hotpink;
    }
</style>
